title: RackZone.ie Heavy Duty Foldable & Stackable Plastic Crate – 600D x 400W x 300H, 59L, Snap Lock, Industrial Garage Storage Box, Durable & Space-Saving, Easy to Clean – Charcoal Grey
features: Space Saving & Versatile Storage Solution - The RackZone.ie storage box is a space saving solution with a collapsible design, folding down to 72mm–92mm to save up to 70% space. Perfect for homes, offices, and garages, these stackable storage boxes keep items organised. Use them as storage baskets for essentials or toy storage for kids’ rooms. Durable and versatile, our storage boxes offer the perfect blend of convenience and efficiency.

Secure Stacking with Easy Access - Our Plastic storage box features an interlocking nesting system, ensuring stackable storage without shifting. The unique open-side access lets you retrieve items even when stacked, eliminating the need to unstack everything. Perfect for organising plastic storage boxes in homes, offices, and garages, it also works great for food storage or as a versatile plastic box for various needs.

Heavy Duty & Durable Construction - Made from high-strength, eco-friendly plastic, this collapsible storage box is built to handle heavy loads from 60kg to 90kg. Manufactured using a blowing process, it offers superior strength over standard injection-molded crates, making it perfect for industrial use, transport, and storage. Ideal as a toy box storage solution, shelf organiser, or for storage boxes for shelves, this organiser box ensures durability and efficiency.

Safe & User-Friendly for All Environments - Designed with smooth, rounded edges, this plastic storage basket eliminates injury risks from sharp components. Free from screws, nails, or harmful materials, it’s perfect for food storage, vegetable storage, pharmaceuticals, electronics, and delicate items. The easy-to-clean surface ensures hygiene and durability. Ideal for kitchens, warehouses, and homes, these plastic boxes double as heavy-duty storage boxes and potato storage solutions.

Versatile for Multiple Uses - Whether you need a black storage box for tools, seasonal decorations, groceries, or office supplies, this crate is a must-have solution. Its plastic storage design is both lightweight and sturdy, making it perfect for home organisation, business storage, travel, and industrial use. Use it as a plastic basket for easy basket storage or as a pantry storage solution to keep essentials neatly organised.
